<h2 class="bold font-l">Moon Spiral Heart Attack</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Video of the trope image. Sailor Moon slams her opponent with a giant heart that shatters on impact and annihilates the target. </p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="a2p5k7" data-video-descrip="Birdo blows a pink heart kiss, which summons a balloon to defeat opponents by carrying them offstage." data-video-title="Birdo" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/a2p5k7_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/pmcs_birdo_2.png" data-video-trope="Main/HeartBeatDown" data-video-tropename="Heart Beat-Down" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="VideoGame/PaperMarioColorSplash" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/pmcs_birdo_2.png">
