<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="ho1tgf" data-video-descrip="Peach powers up for her offensive Super Peach Spin, a curved ball shaped like a heart that causes opponents to charge the net, and her defensive Sweet Kiss Return that blows a heart like a kiss to retrieve the ball for her. " data-video-title="Peach's Special Moves - Mario Power Tennis" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/ho1tgf_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/ho1tgf.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/HeartBeatDown" data-video-tropename="Heart Beat-Down" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Franchise/SuperMarioBros,VideoGame/MarioPowerTennis" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/ho1tgf.jpg">
